Purpose: Describes event producers, broker queues/exchanges, and consumers.\par
\f1
```mermaid\par
flowchart LR\par
  AUTH["AuthService"] -->|"notifications, kyc events"| MQ[(RabbitMQ)]\par
  WAL["WalletService"] -->|"wallet_transfer, wallet_topup, notifications"| MQ\par
  ADM["AdminService"] -->|"kyc decisions / admin events"| MQ\par
  REW["RewardService"] -->|"reward events"| MQ\par
\par
