\par
\b 8) Sequence Diagram (Transfer with PIN + Email)\b0\par
Purpose: Step-by-step flow of secure transfer with PIN validation and email notification.\par
\f1
```mermaid\par
sequenceDiagram\par
  actor U as User\par
  participant FE as Frontend\par
  participant GW as Gateway\par
  participant WS as WalletService\par
  participant AS as AuthService\par
  participant MQ as RabbitMQ\par
  participant NS as NotificationService\par
  participant SMTP as SMTP\par
\par
  U->>FE: Enter transfer + PIN\par
  FE->>GW: POST /api/wallet/transfer\par
  GW->>WS: Forward request\par
  WS->>AS: POST /internal/user/{id}/pin/verify\par
  AS-->>WS: PIN valid\par
  WS->>WS: Debit sender / credit receiver\par
  WS->>MQ: Publish transfer + notification events\par
  WS-->>GW: Transfer success\par
  GW-->>FE: Response success\par
  MQ->>NS: Consume notification event\par
  NS->>SMTP: Send email (includes sender/recipient name)\par
  SMTP-->>U: Transaction email delivered\par
```\par
